</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</td></tr></table>
<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="M.C3.A9moire_politique_:_Patrick_Bloche.2C_d.C3.A9put.C3.A9"><a href="/wiki/Memoire_politique" title="Memoire politique" class="mw-redirect">Mémoire politique</a>&#160;: Patrick Bloche, député</span></h2>
<div class="floatright"><a href="/wiki/File:PatrickBloche.jpg" class="image" title="Patrick Bloche"><img alt="Patrick Bloche" src="/wiki/images/4/48/PatrickBloche.jpg" width="150" height="192" /></a></div>
